The Korean drama 100 Days My Prince Sub Indo tells the story of a man named Lee Yool played by Do Kyung Soo who is a Crown Prince of the Kingdom and has everything he has. One day he mysteriously fell from a cliff and suffered a very serious injury.

When awakened Lee Yool suffered a memory loss where he changed into a person named Won Deuk, who has the opposite nature of Lee Yool. Meanwhile, Hong Sim played by Nam Ji Hyun is a very smart woman and is the first woman to manage a private detective agency in Joseon. One day they met and made a story together for 100 days.
